WEBVTT

00:00:10.559 --> 00:00:16.995
Yesterday I saw the whole sky was filled with color and light.

00:00:18.296 --> 00:00:20.687
As you know that vibrations have light.

00:00:24.083 --> 00:00:28.169
It’s very light flickering, very small light,

00:00:28.169 --> 00:00:34.076
each particle of vibration has and you can see that.

00:00:35.135 --> 00:00:43.116
But when there are too many, then they can be caught up by your cameras.

00:00:43.814 --> 00:00:48.195
But yesterday I think the clouds got vibrated.

00:00:50.559 --> 00:00:54.640
And is a very great thing to get the clouds vibrated.

00:00:54.640 --> 00:00:57.697
If the clouds are vibrated, the rain will be vibrated.

00:00:58.492 --> 00:01:03.639
If the rain is vibrated, the land will be vibrated.

00:01:04.577 --> 00:01:13.612
All the crops that are to be germinated will be vibrated too,

00:01:14.720 --> 00:01:19.200
so when it goes into the body of human beings,

00:01:19.200 --> 00:01:24.902
they’ll get also vibrations. Is the best way now is to
vibrate the clouds, I think,

00:01:24.902 --> 00:01:27.431
if you have to have many more people for Sahaja Yoga.

00:01:30.320 --> 00:01:35.769
That’s the idea came into My mind last night that why not vibrate all the clouds,

00:01:35.769 --> 00:01:36.775
that’s the best way.

00:01:41.119 --> 00:01:45.479
Moreover the vibrations are 

00:01:46.640 --> 00:01:56.758
very tiny bit, with one point going into a half circle normally.

00:01:58.807 --> 00:02:04.331
This half circle then combines to make “Om” sometimes, 

00:02:04.596 --> 00:02:06.610
sometimes it makes a chain,

00:02:07.221 --> 00:02:11.825
sometimes it gathers together to make crosses.

00:02:11.825 --> 00:02:17.465
But the basic thing about them is that they can think,

00:02:20.480 --> 00:02:25.917
and think very fast, much faster than human beings can think.

00:02:25.917 --> 00:02:29.997
extremely collective extremely
collective.

00:02:30.720 --> 00:02:35.080
So they move together,

00:02:35.760 --> 00:02:37.137
thinking the same way,

00:02:37.137 --> 00:02:40.445
understanding the same way in an absolute manner

00:02:40.654 --> 00:02:47.374
manner and work out the whole thing in a
very beautiful

00:02:47.711 --> 00:02:50.830
 silent way that you cannot even feel.

00:03:00.664 --> 00:03:10.397
Today we have assembled here to celebrate the Sahasrara Day 

00:03:11.680 --> 00:03:18.331
which was opened in 1970 on this date.

00:03:19.680 --> 00:03:32.481
I find this beautiful canopy is like our Sahasrara.

00:03:37.033 --> 00:03:46.032
And [it’s] so very apt to have this beautiful arrangement for Sahasrara Day.

00:03:53.120 --> 00:03:58.745
We have to understand what happens when the Sahasrara opens.

00:04:02.239 --> 00:04:08.716
When the Kundalini passes through the five centres 

00:04:08.716 --> 00:04:15.920
it enters into the area which we call as limbic area. 

00:04:15.920 --> 00:04:23.680
This area is all surrounded by thousand nerves

00:04:23.680 --> 00:04:33.433
and when these nerves get enlightened they look like flames of VIBGYOR colours,

00:04:33.433 --> 00:04:41.445
seven colours, and very mildly, beautifully shining,

00:04:45.360 --> 00:04:48.919
emitting peace.

00:04:50.880 --> 00:05:02.594
But when the Kundalini starts emitting its vibration on the sides

00:05:14.527 --> 00:05:26.423
 all these nerves get enlightened gradually and start moving on all directions,

00:05:28.000 --> 00:05:32.199
opening the Sahasrara 

00:05:33.600 --> 00:05:45.124
and then the Kundalini emerges out 

00:05:50.240 --> 00:05:57.174
emerges out through the fontanelle bone area, 

00:05:57.174 --> 00:06:00.097
which we call as ‘Brahmarandhra’.

00:06:01.759 --> 00:06:10.294
‘Randhra’ means the ‘hole’ and the ‘Brahma’ is the All-Pervading Power of God’s love.

00:06:13.039 --> 00:06:21.489
So it enters into the subtle energy,

00:06:22.115 --> 00:06:26.462
 which is all-pervading, which we do not feel normally. 

00:06:28.148 --> 00:06:32.646
But then the chaitanya, 

00:06:34.639 --> 00:06:36.062
 the vibrations, 

00:06:37.241 --> 00:06:49.692
which are the part and parcel of this energy, 

00:06:49.692 --> 00:06:51.840
All-Pervading Power,

00:06:51.840 --> 00:06:53.569
 the Paramchaitanya,

00:06:56.800 --> 00:07:10.328
they start entering into our brain and showering their blessings in the limbic area they assemble.

00:07:14.960 --> 00:07:21.194
Now the limbic area is connected to all the area of the brain

00:07:22.663 --> 00:07:25.000
and also to the nerves.

00:07:29.039 --> 00:07:33.280
So it starts flowing onto the nerves

00:07:35.520 --> 00:07:42.875
 giving you the new awareness of collective consciousness, called as ‘samuhik chetana’.

00:07:44.513 --> 00:07:47.819
So, you get a new chetana, a new awareness, 

00:07:49.563 --> 00:07:57.965
which is showered upon your limbic area. 

00:08:01.840 --> 00:08:08.361
The working of these chaitanya waves is very interesting. 

00:08:10.770 --> 00:08:18.949
They are normally formed like small commas,

00:08:20.466 --> 00:08:24.716
 but then they go into different forms. 

00:08:27.280 --> 00:08:38.108
They make themselves into swastikas as the four-limbed symbol of innocence 

00:08:42.080 --> 00:08:47.821
or they become the Omkara: as you know how ‘Om’ is written, 

00:08:50.560 --> 00:09:00.344
which is the symbol of our doing, our awareness.

00:09:02.880 --> 00:09:15.306
So, when they form the swastika they try to nourish the left side 

00:09:16.221 --> 00:09:24.001
 and when they form the Omkara they nourish the right side: left and right sympathetic nervous systems they nourish.

00:09:28.240 --> 00:09:35.815
But Sahasrara to be kept open,

00:09:36.258 --> 00:09:42.177
is rather difficult for people because it’s a vicious circle. 

00:09:43.839 --> 00:09:50.838
First, these vibrations should enter into your brain through the Brahmarandhra 

00:09:51.777 --> 00:09:55.579
when it is opened out

00:09:55.579 --> 00:10:03.006
and they should nourish your nerves by which your left and right side open out 

00:10:05.279 --> 00:10:13.560
and so more chaitanya can flow down all these centres.

00:10:13.760 --> 00:10:21.012
But if your Sahasrara is not properly opened

00:10:21.012 --> 00:10:23.915
 this process doesn’t take place.

00:10:26.320 --> 00:10:31.050
As a result of that the chakras don’t open,

00:10:32.640 --> 00:10:45.754
the Kundalini only as very few strands is kept in the spinal cord 

00:10:46.870 --> 00:10:58.480
and the new strands cannot rise because your chakras are not open. 

00:10:58.480 --> 00:11:06.130
So, in Sahaja Yoga, it is very important to keep your Sahasrara open.

00:11:07.310 --> 00:11:09.167
Otherwise, there’s a vicious circle.

00:11:20.720 --> 00:11:26.200
Can you tell us what the vibrations are?

00:11:46.280 --> 00:11:51.336
Vibrations, as I said, that is the manifestation of the Spirit.

00:11:52.282 --> 00:12:00.000
But it is a very vague way of expressing it. Now see, if there’s a nice flame before me, 

00:12:00.795 --> 00:12:05.053
This candle has been enlightened. Now what does it do?

00:12:06.488 --> 00:12:11.788
It gives you light. Alright, but how does it give you light?

00:12:13.440 --> 00:12:16.537
By throwing light towards you, by emitting light.

00:12:17.440 --> 00:12:22.491
It is the emitting, of pulsation from
the Self.

00:12:25.920 --> 00:12:28.961
This light, this is light. Actually there is sound,

00:12:28.961 --> 00:12:32.364
there is light; very high frequency
sound – very high frequency.

00:12:33.003 --> 00:12:38.549
Actually many types of sounds are mixed in. There’s is magnetism in this, in these vibrations.

00:12:38.681 --> 00:12:45.801
It has all the five elements -the subtle of all the five elements (tanmatras) inside these vibrations only.

00:12:46.880 --> 00:12:51.609
They are talking, they are telling you,
they are guiding you, they are helping you.

00:12:52.050 --> 00:12:54.736
It’s because the Spirit is working through them. 

00:12:55.242 --> 00:12:58.294
Like this light that you take in your hand: you go in the darkness,

00:13:00.146 --> 00:13:04.332
and you see that there is an impediment in between [and] you have to cross it.

00:13:05.499 --> 00:13:07.456
So you get the idea with this light.

00:13:09.440 --> 00:13:12.300
The light is doing that for you.

00:13:12.762 --> 00:13:19.456
So the vibrations are actually the things which are the doers and the enjoyers.

00:13:20.154 --> 00:13:25.289
They are the one, who enjoy, also, if they find a very good Self-realised soul coming.

00:13:25.289 --> 00:13:30.000
Then you just feel the Self-realised soul and you say, “Oh very good. Come along, come along.

00:13:30.000 --> 00:13:34.560
Just have it.” Everybody starts enjoying 

00:13:34.560 --> 00:13:39.660
that joy that’s coming from that person. And that is what it is,

00:13:39.660 --> 00:13:46.813
that you start enjoying that beauty in that person through the vibrations.

00:13:46.813 --> 00:13:53.272
It’s a multi- dimensional thing – though it looks so simple, that you are feeling in the hand, that’s all.

00:13:53.360 --> 00:13:57.217
So it is a multi-dimensional thing just like the God Almighty.

00:13:57.217 --> 00:14:00.944
And, for your information, it is only He does everything.

00:14:00.944 --> 00:14:06.009
So only the vibrations work out everything. We really do not do anything whatsoever

00:14:06.009 --> 00:14:08.921
– [if we think we do] we are living in a fool’s paradise!

00:14:15.360 --> 00:14:20.362
But these vibrations only, which connect you with the All-pervading Power,

00:14:20.362 --> 00:14:27.773
which are part of the All-pervading power, these pervading Almighty’s eyes, you can say

00:14:27.773 --> 00:14:37.795
– they are the ones who look after each and every minute thing in this whole world. Can you think of such a multi-dimensional thing?

00:14:39.279 --> 00:14:44.103
Now you have seen how vibrations work on people, how they
dissolve even the thick bones

00:14:44.103 --> 00:14:49.522
and how they bring out the Kundalini here and how you see the softness on your head.

00:14:49.522 --> 00:14:55.000
Just you cannot explain how, because they only do everything.

00:14:55.264 --> 00:14:59.802
 They have the universal communication centres

00:14:59.802 --> 00:15:05.847
and they have universal broadcasting
stations, they have universal TV centres there.

00:15:05.847 --> 00:15:13.768
Everything is there. In short, you just copy
them a little bit and you think you are doing something

00:15:13.768 --> 00:15:16.838
but you really don’t do anything
whatsoever.

00:15:20.240 --> 00:15:24.199
That’s why it is said that Brahma – this is the expression of Brahma,

00:15:24.199 --> 00:15:32.730
these vibrations are the Brahma – is the only Truth, the rest is all Mithya，is all a maya, is just an illusion.

00:15:32.730 --> 00:15:35.000
We live in illusions you see. 

00:15:38.240 --> 00:15:43.199
He is the Enjoyer, He is the Doer, you are just in between to see Him.

00:15:43.199 --> 00:15:48.613
It would be like this mic (microphone) thinking that he’s giving the lecture of Sahaja Yoga – it’s really like that!!

00:15:56.800 --> 00:16:03.759
So to explain what is vibrations may not be 

00:16:04.160 --> 00:16:08.548
so simple in all its details. 

00:16:08.548 --> 00:16:12.381
But the overall idea I have given to you. Is it alright?

00:16:20.160 --> 00:16:27.260
As it is you know Sahaja Yoga, is a living process. And it grows both ways:

00:16:27.260 --> 00:16:32.255
upwards and downwards. In the beginning it grows more downwards.

00:16:32.255 --> 00:16:38.016
And in the downwards process, we have to depend on our vibrations very much.

00:16:38.016 --> 00:16:44.255
We must all the time remember that we are realised-souls, that we have got vibrations.

00:16:44.761 --> 00:16:48.819
This is the way we have to judge. This is the way we have to understand.

00:16:48.819 --> 00:16:56.235
The vibration is the only way that we’ll know others; not by something

00:16:56.235 --> 00:17:02.952
[like] you will feel that the person looks very sweet and nice and a snake may come out of that person.

00:17:03.040 --> 00:17:08.636
So best is, to judge a person through vibrations. Judge everything through vibrations,

00:17:08.636 --> 00:17:15.176
not through your own understanding or superficial methods of judging others.

00:17:15.925 --> 00:17:20.184
Now, there are also so many conditionings we have got, by which we judge others.

00:17:20.184 --> 00:17:25.593
And these conditionings can also bias our judgment.

00:17:25.791 --> 00:17:32.975
So best way is to see the vibrations. Through vibrations you will have the real knowledge about what is happening.

00:17:33.723 --> 00:17:37.787
Now many people, in the beginning, also start misguiding.

00:17:38.337 --> 00:17:43.216
So best is to develop your
vibrations. For that you have to grow inward first of all.

00:17:43.943 --> 00:17:47.047
If you grow inward, deeply,

00:17:47.289 --> 00:17:53.883
then what will happen is that outward growth will be very solid and would be exact.

00:18:02.049 --> 00:18:12.012
the principle of Ganesha is extremely subtle, is the subtlest of subtle. And it exists in everything,

00:18:12.977 --> 00:18:17.843
that it exists in the matter in the form of vibrations.

00:18:18.328 --> 00:18:22.709
There is no matter which is
without vibrations.

00:18:23.435 --> 00:18:38.356
It has vibrations which are seen even in the atoms and also in the
molecules of all matter that is existing.

00:18:39.083 --> 00:18:45.840
And what makes you – the feeling that we are now a means,

00:18:46.236 --> 00:18:53.317
a means, we can say, an instrument, a media, by which we express the Ganesha Tattwa all over,

00:18:53.669 --> 00:18:55.000
that is vibrations.

00:18:55.914 --> 00:18:58.927
So the vibrations itself about which you are asking,

00:18:59.125 --> 00:19:04.285
these vibrations themselves are
nothing but the Principle of Shri Ganesha. He is Omkara.

00:19:05.320 --> 00:19:14.576
And when it is, then what is it, that feeling as I told you, the vatsalya, the feeling of love between a child and the mother.

00:19:15.479 --> 00:19:19.462
That feeling, it is the one that is vibrations,

00:19:21.135 --> 00:19:28.134
between the child and the mother. The distance between the two is vibrations,

00:19:28.134 --> 00:19:34.740
and that’s what one has to feel – that he’s a child still and there’s the mother

00:19:34.960 --> 00:19:41.767
and mother is bringing the child, giving all the powers to the child,

00:19:41.767 --> 00:19:48.960
bringing up, loving the child, understanding the limitations of the child, looking after, all that.

00:19:48.960 --> 00:19:55.514
 All the sweetness, all the wisdom of the child to be appreciated.

00:19:56.263 --> 00:19:57.619
That is vibrations.

00:19:58.016 --> 00:20:04.416
So all the relationships that are between human beings and God, are through the Ganesha Principle.

00:20:05.120 --> 00:20:12.130
So when it becomes the relationship between you and God, then there are vibrations.

00:20:12.240 --> 00:20:18.079
And then that same relationship should extend to everything that you do.

00:20:18.079 --> 00:20:23.675
You should see what things are good, whatever has got vibrations.

00:20:24.424 --> 00:20:31.065
Today I want to tell you something very important about this All-Pervading Power we heard about.

00:20:31.362 --> 00:20:36.626
These are nothing but vibrations. This Paramachaitanya is nothing but vibrations,

00:20:36.626 --> 00:20:43.520
where all identities are lost – where the mother is lost, father is lost, we can say, nothing remains,

00:20:43.520 --> 00:20:53.444
then it is just these vibrations, this subtle vatsalya exists. That’s all.

00:20:54.016 --> 00:21:01.664
And this is the only thing, out of which everything comes and remains in itself.

00:21:02.632 --> 00:21:04.194
Everything is inside that.

00:21:04.898 --> 00:21:08.513
This Paramachaitanya has got everything inside this.

00:21:08.711 --> 00:21:16.862
So we can say that everything is nothing but knowledge, is nothing but truth, is nothing but light.

00:21:16.862 --> 00:21:28.675
But when the folds of these come out, then we get into the folds of that Chaitanya and then we become ignorant.

00:21:28.675 --> 00:21:34.076
But there is nothing like ignorance. It doesn’t exist, it doesn’t exist. 

00:21:34.076 --> 00:21:41.753
Like there is darkness because there’s no light. Once light comes, it doesn’t exist it doesn’t exist.

00:21:41.753 --> 00:21:44.097
 So ignorance doesn’t exist. 

00:21:44.097 --> 00:21:52.034
But what happens that the folds of this ocean, into that people go and it is lost.

00:21:53.705 --> 00:21:59.077
Thus we understand one thing very clearly: that we are in Paramchaitanya. 

00:21:59.077 --> 00:22:03.797
We are made by Paramchaitanya, all the time we are surrounded by it.

00:22:03.797 --> 00:22:09.226
Only thing is, we are sometimes lost in the folds. And why? 

00:22:09.226 --> 00:22:23.272
Why we are lost in the folds is because of our own – our own unawareness.

00:22:23.272 --> 00:22:30.000
This awareness has to come: that we are part and parcel of that Paramachaitanya. 

00:22:30.432 --> 00:22:44.752
The whole thing is called as chidvilasa, is the vilas, is the playful enjoyment of God’s Attention.

00:22:45.646 --> 00:22:55.023
In the same way, this Paramachaitanya acts and what we get lost is, in our awareness, that we are Paramachaitanya. 

00:22:55.023 --> 00:23:04.168
 That’s why the play starts, the play starts like yesterday’s – day before yesterday’s Puja, what did we do? 

00:23:04.766 --> 00:23:14.298
We were sitting there and it started raining. So – to prove, to prove that I can control rain. 

00:23:14.798 --> 00:23:19.390
So it rained. Some people were covering up, some thing, this thing. 

00:23:19.390 --> 00:23:25.338
I gave a bandhan. After some time, the rain moved out from the Puja to the back side.

00:23:26.596 --> 00:23:33.063
It was not raining where you were sitting. And after that, it became the sun and it was so clouded. 

00:23:33.236 --> 00:23:41.481
Sun came, it was, became sunny, so that’s how you have to become aware of the powers of Chaitanya. 

00:23:42.211 --> 00:23:46.976
Now when you give bandhan, what you do is to put the Chaitanya into action,

00:23:47.349 --> 00:23:57.071
“Now act here, act there, act here.” Though you are, supposing, in the ocean, but the ocean acts on you all the time. 

00:23:57.071 --> 00:24:03.047
You cannot act on the ocean, you cannot ask water to do this and do that. But as realised souls,

00:24:03.047 --> 00:24:08.244
you are empowered, now you can ask water, “Alright, you dissolve this, you do this, you do that.” 

00:24:10.060 --> 00:24:17.449
But for that, it is important to be the masters. And to become the masters, you see – like a matter becomes a human being,

00:24:17.449 --> 00:24:22.866
and from human being, you have to become the masters of the matter and you handle the matter. 

00:24:23.500 --> 00:24:28.411
So ordeals do not remain because you give a bandhan, it works out. 

00:24:28.411 --> 00:24:36.844
So in every action, in everything, whatever you do, you should know it is the Paramachaitanya that acts. 

00:24:36.844 --> 00:24:44.693
Only thing you have to be aware of yourself, and aware of it, it acts; and you just jump into that awareness and it works. 

00:24:46.763 --> 00:24:56.181
And that you have seen. But still, so many people do not know. So many people still, though they know through their brains,  

00:24:56.181 --> 00:24:57.432
do not know in their hearts.

00:24:57.432 --> 00:25:02.312
And so many people, even if they know in their hearts, they do not act in their attention. 

00:25:02.312 --> 00:25:09.470
So only these three things you have to improve: is one is your head, another is your heart and third is your liver.

00:25:09.470 --> 00:25:13.888
 If you can improve these three organs, this Paramachaitanya will act. 

00:25:18.935 --> 00:25:25.060
The question is, what is the importance of spreading the vibrations in the environment.

00:25:25.124 --> 00:25:31.521
Like if we speak of scientists, they say that electromagnetic vibrations are there,

00:25:31.521 --> 00:25:35.360
the electromagnetic vibrations perform a function.

00:25:35.360 --> 00:25:41.720
So we can say to them that these vibrations that we have as a result of Sahaja Yoga

00:25:41.732 --> 00:25:45.400
is flowing through us and is doing something for the environment.

00:25:45.617 --> 00:25:50.063
So if you can please say something about what it does to the environment.

00:25:50.385 --> 00:25:54.965
Now electromagnetic vibrations are the right sided vibrations are,

00:25:55.084 --> 00:25:58.080
of the dead, we shall say.

00:25:58.088 --> 00:26:02.700
Now our vibrations are what we are calling this Chaitanya,

00:26:02.700 --> 00:26:06.180
is the combination of all these three 

00:26:06.380 --> 00:26:10.740
plus the “Ardha Matra” [or “Ardha Bindu” is the semicircle; together with the “Bindu” they represent the Adi Shakti in Om]

00:26:10.740 --> 00:26:17.220
 is the Adi Shakti on top of that. So we have four types of vibrations [A, U, M and the Ardha Matra on top]

00:26:17.220 --> 00:26:26.145
integrated in these vibrations: emotional side, evolutionary and the one that is electromagnetic.

00:26:26.772 --> 00:26:30.719
So we have all these vibrations within us integrated, 

00:26:31.649 --> 00:26:39.400
and on top of that is the fourth one which is the Adi Shakti’s vibrations.

00:26:39.735 --> 00:26:49.619
 They organise, they think, they work out, they direct, they choose, they do everything which is the administrative side.

00:26:52.039 --> 00:26:54.419
So we have four types of
vibrations within us.

00:27:00.759 --> 00:27:13.411
So in Sahaja Yoga when we desire something, we must know what we desire, first fix your goal and then relate it to that.

00:27:14.592 --> 00:27:26.925
The first destroying factor that is within us is the Shri Ganesha’s power and this Shri Ganesha is the power of Mahakali.

00:27:28.423 --> 00:27:34.009
She first planted Shri Ganesha to emit holiness on this Earth,

00:27:35.264 --> 00:27:42.543
so the whole thing could be vibrated and as you know one aspect of Shri Ganesha is also Omkara,

00:27:43.638 --> 00:27:48.260
means this vibratory awareness which flows everywhere.

00:27:48.760 --> 00:28:07.645
So these vibrations have four sides in it: one is that these vibrations establish holiness, auspiciousness through Mahakali;

00:28:07.645 --> 00:28:16.872
then these same vibrations also comfort us through Mahakali power. 

00:28:18.259 --> 00:28:26.368
Vibrations do not give you desires as such, if you see, they do not give you desires,

00:28:27.405 --> 00:28:33.222
 but they give you proof of your desires being fulfilled.

00:28:33.942 --> 00:28:41.202
Supposing you want somebody to be cured, this is your desire and you give vibrations to that person; 

00:28:41.202 --> 00:28:57.884
so its a means, so it is also the action part which is there in those vibrations, but this action also comes from desire.

00:28:57.884 --> 00:29:06.040
So for all Sahaja Yogis it is necessary to first of all early in the morning, while taking the name of Ganesha, 

00:29:06.040 --> 00:29:15.230
must say what is my desire, this is my goal, this is what it is, all activity must be surrendered for this work.

00:29:15.230 --> 00:29:25.120
Weakness of the Mooladhara makes you imbalanced and in that imbalance,  you lose your will.

00:29:25.200 --> 00:29:30.040
So one has to be very careful that our Mooladhara must be fixed properly.

00:29:32.391 --> 00:29:39.640
There are so many ways by which you can fix up your Mooladhara and you must fix up your Mooladhara first;

00:29:39.840 --> 00:29:49.680
then your desire absolutely moves like a kite moves in the sky, stuck to Mooladhara 

00:29:49.680 --> 00:29:52.680
and you can move into any direction to any height, 

00:29:52.680 --> 00:29:57.800
wherever you go you are quite in charge, you know how you are moving. 

00:30:00.785 --> 00:30:03.797
It can bind your attention, everything. 

00:30:03.797 --> 00:30:13.974
So what we say that the roots are very important first to be established for the growth of your desire upward, like a tree.

00:30:15.784 --> 00:30:25.455
So they go hand in hand, Mahakali power and Ganesha’s power go hand in hand because that’s the foundation;

00:30:26.104 --> 00:30:35.693
if it is based on that foundation, desires grow much stronger and stronger and effective and they do not deviate.

00:30:38.088 --> 00:30:47.677
 Every sort of desire is fulfilled till you reach that state where there’s no other desire left but to enjoy, 

00:30:48.001 --> 00:30:52.801
you just enjoy, without any desire, desirelessly you enjoy.

00:30:57.398 --> 00:31:01.262
And that state is to be enjoyed, just to be enjoyed.

00:31:02.280 --> 00:31:04.018
May God bless you!
